# bsi-production (BSI)

The `bsi-production/` folder contains the production website for blazesportsintel.com.

## Structure
```
bsi-production/
├── index.html          # Main entry point
├── worker.js           # Cloudflare Worker
├── wrangler.toml       # Worker config
├── manifest.json       # PWA manifest
├── sw.js               # Service worker
├── images/             # Static images (personal photos, logos)
├── src/
│   ├── styles/tokens/  # Design tokens (colors, typography, spacing)
│   ├── lib/graphics/   # 3D graphics engine
│   └── components/3d/  # React 3D components
├── blaze-blitz/        # Football game (Vite + TypeScript)
└── docs/               # Graphics integration docs
```

## Design tokens
Located in `src/styles/tokens/`:
- `colors.ts` — Brand color palette
- `typography.ts` — Font system
- `spacing.ts` — Spacing scale
- `animation.ts` — Animation timings

## Deployment
```bash
# Deploy the worker
cd bsi-production && ./deploy.sh
# or
wrangler deploy --config bsi-production/wrangler.toml
```

